, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Melbourne's Yarra River is set to undergo a rebrand of a similar nature.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rebrand\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar nature\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since forming in 2020,Regen Melbourneand a committed group of researchers, environmental advocates, Indigenous leaders, engineers, entrepreneurs, and environmentalists have been hatching a plan to make Melbourne's Birrarung (Yarra) River swimmable.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birrarung\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2020,Regen Melbourneand\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"a committed group\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental advocates\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"Indigenous leaders\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"engineers\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"entrepreneurs\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"environmentalists\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B&T spoke with Regen's CEO, Kaj Lofgren, about how he and his team are tackling this mammoth goal.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B&T\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Regen's CEO\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"Kaj Lofgren\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"this mammoth goal\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We started to ask the question: how can we be useful?\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are conscious that we are all members of too many online communities that maybe do not push us to do much - we did not want to be just another network,\\\" said Lofgren.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"too many online communities\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"just another network\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most social and environmental goals are heavily constricted by funding, culture, and imagination.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most social and environmental goals\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"imagination\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are the issues we were trying to fight against.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We asked our partners to think about solutions as if none of these constraints existed - and the river kept coming up!\\\"\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"solutions\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"these constraints\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It came up from different angles, namely as a source of deep connection for many Victorians\\\".\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\", \"score\": 0.9999996986648966, \"rank\": 1.788139042476567e-07, \"text\": \"Victorians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different angles\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"deep connection\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But also, in a pragmatic sense, most of the water we drink comes from the river,\\\" added Lofgren.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pragmatic sense\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of creating a swimmable corridor from source to sea, Dights Falls to Port Phillip Bay, preoccupied the minds of Lofgren and the Regen Melbourne Alliance.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dights Falls\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\"}, {\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Port Phillip Bay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\", \"score\": 0.6881450014984589, \"rank\": 0.4531821023511726, \"text\": \"Alliance\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimmable corridor\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"source\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"sea\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"the minds\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swimmable Birrarung initiative is part of a growing global trend of city river cleanups, namely the highly publicised cleanup of the Seine River ahead of the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547353592, \"rank\": 4.52646518360049e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Swimmable Birrarung initiative\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"a growing global trend\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"city river cleanups\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"namely the highly publicised cleanup\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around \\u20ac1.4b (AUD $2.3b) has resulted in the water now being bacteria-free 90 per cent of the time.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria-free 90 per cent\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, it was ravaged by E. coli and enterococci.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"E. coli\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"enterococci\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The cleanup of the Seine River is deeply inspiring.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cleanup\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both because of the successful outcome, a swimmable river, but also at a broader level - it's a reminder we can do big things when we put our minds to it,\\\" said Lofgren.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the successful outcome\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimmable river\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"a broader level\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"big things\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"our minds\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oslo, Copenhagen, Vienna, Switzerland, and closer to home, Sydney's Parramatta River, are all success stories of urban river swimming.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\", \"score\": 0.9999976682452043, \"rank\": 2.2867256268343173e-06, \"text\": \"Oslo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\", \"score\": 0.9999999085744136, \"rank\": 5.099983380704096e-08, \"text\": \"Copenhagen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\"}, {\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"score\": 0.9999990926680336, \"rank\": 9.07328447954746e-07, \"text\": \"Vienna\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999912445133702, \"rank\": 8.155036062615158e-06, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999878000388215, \"rank\": 1.2160825851777794e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"success stories\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"urban river swimming\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nursing yourself in water is perhaps the most visceral way of being reminded of the fact that we are nature.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"the most visceral way\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no other feeling like that,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no other feeling\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have worked in many complex project environments where burnout and overwhelm are high, and that's the first thing that stops meaningful action,\\\" Lofgren said.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many complex project environments\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"burnout\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"overwhelm\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the first thing\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"meaningful action\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To counter this, Lofgren and his team created six fields of action that made the Swimmable Birrarung initiative more digestible.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birrarung\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lofgren\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"six fields\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fields of action also allow partners to quickly get involved by recognising how their skills can best be used.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fields\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"their skills\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fields are storytelling, legal and policy, water health, business and enterprise, campaigns, building a movement, and swimming activations.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fields\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"policy\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"water health\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"enterprise\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"campaigns\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"a movement\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming activations\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To build a movement, Regen Melbourne partnered with Yarra Riverkeeper Association (YRKA) on the Birrarung Riverfest, a 3-week-long celebration of the Birrarung River and its importance to the city.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Me